fi.yussiv.minigolf.domain

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.geom.Point2D
      • java.awt.Point
        • fi.yussiv.minigolf.domain.Position
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class Position
extends Point
    Extension of java.awt.Point that retains floating point values unchanged. The original saves the values as integers, which leads to unwanted flooring when ball movement is slow.
    See Also:
